266
00:20:43,541 --> 00:20:45,791
Oh! I almost forgot.

267
00:20:46,708 --> 00:20:47,958
There was one yesterday.

268
00:20:48,041 --> 00:20:50,501
You want to see it?
I wrote it down like you said.

269
00:20:50,833 --> 00:20:52,923
