01:13:49,500 --> 01:13:50,330
Hi.

1008
01:13:50,500 --> 01:13:51,330
Hey.

1009
01:13:51,500 --> 01:13:52,330
Who's here?

1010
01:13:52,708 --> 01:13:54,418
- We're all here.
